[|] [=Macro]

[|] assert
[table:end]

[para]
[:en] The contents are the same as the Standard C library header [`<assert.h>].
[:zh_CN] 其内容与标准 C 程序库头文件 [`<assert.h>] 相同。

[para:xref]
[:en] ISO C 7.2.
[:zh_CN] ISO C 7.2。
